Special Note for Sound Effects ("sounds" directory):

The audio files included in this project (assets/sounds directory) are extracted from the NES game Arkanoid,
as provided by The Sounds Resource (https://www.sounds-resource.com/nes/arkanoid/sound/3698/).
They are made available only for personal, non-commercial use, fan projects, and testing purposes.

For any commercial use of the project or redistribution of these sounds, you must use royalty-free sounds
or obtain permission from the copyright holders.

